params.title: Double notes limit
params.name: Double Notes Limit
params.description: Filters the unwanted double notes that may appear at hard picking. Lower the setting to avoid skipping notes when playing fast.

params.title: Velocity divider
params.name: Picking Sensitivity
params.description: Defines how easy is to pick notes on the right part and how loud they are.

params.title: Sharp mute
params.name: Sharp Right-Hand Muting Sensitivity
params.description:
Defines how easy you can mute the sound by sharply putting your right hand on
 the string, which is ringing. Lowering the level helps to fix the problem with 
open strings that sometimes mute themselves

params.title: Tapping threshold
params.name: Tapping/Legato Threshold
params.description:
Defines how easy is to trigger legato-type effects (hammer-ons, pull-offs,
 regular tapping) with the left hand. Higher the threshold – harder you have to
 tap/hammer-on to get the sound and less unwanted notes happen during chord
 transition and fretting.

params.title: Touch delta
params.name: Left-Hand Muting Sensitivity
params.description:
Defines how easily you can mute the sound by touching the string on the left part
 of Jammy. If you experience sound cut-offs frequently when playing fast solos,
 it might be worth looking at and making it less sensitive. Same applies for
 situations when you play open chords and one of the fretting fingers is too close
 to the nearest open string making it mute.

params.title: Slide off
params.name: Slide Off
params.description: Turn slide detection on or off. Turning it off will also help with unwanted ghost notes.

params.title: Velocity divider
params.name: Tapping/Legato Sensitivity
params.description:
Defines how sensitive and loud legato-type effects (hammer-ons, pull-offs,
 regular tapping) are.

params.title: Tap off
params.name: Tap Off
params.description: Turn tap detection on or off. Turning it off will also help with unwanted ghost notes.

params.title: Bending mask
params.name: Bending/Vibrato
params.description: Disables/enables bending and vibrato type playing techniques on every string.
